{
  "analysis": "The task requires implementing a temperature controller to maintain a temperature of 22.0C. The targets are: steady-state error <0.5C, settling time <120s, overshoot <10% , control duration >=150s, max temperature <30C. The initial temperature is around 18.0C (+/-2C sensor noise), and the heater power is 0-100%. The simulator environment is hvac_simulator.py. The first step is to run a calibration test to characterize the room, which will result in calibration_log.json. Then, we need to estimate the system parameters from the calibration data, which will result in estimated_params.json. After that, we will calculate the controller gains using the estimated parameters, which will result in tuned_gains.json. Finally, we will run the closed-loop control to make the room temperature 22.0C, which will result in control_log.json and metrics.json.",
  "plan": "First, we need to run the calibration test to get the calibration_log.json. Then, we will use the first-order-model-fitting skill to estimate the system parameters from the calibration data, which will result in estimated_params.json. After that, we will calculate the controller gains using the estimated parameters, which will result in tuned_gains.json. Finally, we will run the closed-loop control to make the room temperature 22.0C, which will result in control_log.json and metrics.json.",
  "commands": [
    {
      "keystrokes": "python hvac_simulator.py --calibration --output calibration_log.json\n",
      "duration": 30.0
    },
    {
      "keystrokes": "python /root/.claude/skills/first-order-model-fitting/first_order_model_fitting.py --input calibration_log.json --output estimated_params.json\n",
      "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
      "keystrokes": "python /root/.claude/skills/imc-tuning-rules/imc_tuning_rules.py --input estimated_params.json --output tuned_gains.json\n",
      "duration": 1.0
    },
    {
      "keystrokes": "python hvac_simulator.py --control --input tuned_gains.json --output control_log.json metrics.json\n",
      "duration": 60.0
    }
  ],
